17:55.960 --> 17:58.758
-l don't like Scotch.
-lt's okay, it's bourbon.

17:58.960 --> 18:00.359
Oh, all right.

18:05.080 --> 18:06.638
More.

18:10.960 --> 18:12.029
How do you feel now?

18:13.160 --> 18:15.594
-l feel a little better.
-Finish the drink.

18:16.000 --> 18:17.991
Can l put some diet Sprite in it?

18:18.880 --> 18:20.313
Just finish it.

18:24.920 --> 18:27.559
There you go. Now how do you feel?

18:29.480 --> 18:30.674
l feel pretty good.

18:32.920 --> 18:35.639
Like, to hell with her.
Who cares what she thinks?

18:35.840 --> 18:37.478
Perfect.

18:37.680 --> 18:40.831
Now go ask that chick over there
if you can buy her a drink.

18:41.200 --> 18:44.317
Wait a minute. Wait a minute,
that's your big secret? Alcohol?

18:45.640 --> 18:47.596
Don't tell anybody.

18:48.720 --> 18:53.032
-lsn't that just a temporary solution?
-lt's only temporary if you stop drinking.

18:54.440 --> 18:55.793
l like it.

18:59.400 --> 19:01.675
Diet Sprite.

19:09.440 --> 19:10.759
l gotta hand it to you, Alan.

19:10.960 --> 19:14.316
Most guys would be off scallops
for a long time.

19:15.360 --> 19:17.032
l like scallops.

19:17.240 --> 19:19.629
But clearly they don't like you.

19:19.840 --> 19:23.037
l guess you choose your seafood
like you choose your women.

19:23.240 --> 19:24.468
l beg to differ.

19:24.680 --> 19:28.468
When it comes to women,
l make them sick.

19:31.280 --> 19:32.838
Fair enough.

19:33.040 --> 19:35.235
So, what else did we learn tonight?

19:35.440 --> 19:37.476
Well, let's see.

19:37.680 --> 19:41.468
l learned that to overcome my fear
of rejection ingrained in me. . .

19:41.680 --> 19:43.955
. . .by an emotionally distant mother. . .

19:44.160 --> 19:47.357
. . .l need to completely disable
my central nervous system. . .

19:47.560 --> 19:50.757
. . .with semi-lethal quantities
of alcohol.

19:51.400 --> 19:53.152
Bravo.

19:54.600 --> 19:56.591
Hey, Charlie, are you coming to bed
or what?

19:57.000 --> 19:58.399
l'll be there in a second.

19:58.600 --> 20:01.876
-What're you looking at?
-Sorry. Very sorry.

20:03.240 --> 20:04.958
So how've you been?

20:08.440 --> 20:09.589
lt worked.

20:09.800 --> 20:12.633
l am totally humiliated
and l don't care.

20:13.960 --> 20:16.235
You made real progress tonight.
l'm proud of you.

20:16.440 --> 20:20.433
Thanks, Charlie. You're a good teacher
and a good brother.

20:20.640 --> 20:22.278
Thanks.

20:24.680 --> 20:28.878
Well, l guess it's time for me
to go work out my issues.

